Solution 1:

Subproblem:
Let L[i] = max contiguous subsequence sum including ai s.t. 0 <= i <= n

Base case: L[0] = 0

Recurrence:
L[i] = a_i + max(0, L[i-1]) for 1 <= i <= n

Pseudocode
L[0] = 0
curMax = 0
  for i = 1 to n:
    L[i] = a_i + max(L[i-1], 0)
    curMax = max(curMax, L[i])
return curMax

Time complexity is O(n)

